      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Beckoning Slumber",
        "Client": "Exhausted Woman",
        "Description": "I\u0027ve been suffering from\r\ninsomnia... So I figured, hey,\r\nwhy don\u0027t I create a sedative\r\nusing Somnacanth powder?\r\nAt this point, I don\u0027t care how\r\ncrazy it sounds. Just get me\r\nthat powder, please.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Somnacanth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Sommeil envo\u00FBtant",
        "Client": "Femme \u00E9puis\u00E9e",
        "Description": "Je souffre d\u0027insomnie...\r\nAlors je voudrais utiliser\r\nde la poudre de Somnacanth\r\npour faire un s\u00E9datif.\r\nC\u0027est peut-\u00EAtre fou, mais\r\nje m\u0027en moque.\r\nRamenez-moi cette poudre !",
